data.description:
Welcome to your next home in Belton! This adorable ranch is move in ready! You will love the large lot and this move in ready home! Inside, the updated paint and flooring make every room feel like a breath of fresh air. The large, spacious living room flows into an open dining area off the the kitchen that is loaded with cabinets. Plus, there's no shortage of room here – spacious bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and a separate laundry area make life a breeze. Currently the secondary bedrooms are used as hobby spaces but there is plenty of room to accommodate bedroom sets.

But it's not just the inside that shines – this place boasts almost half an acre of land. Soak up the sun on the patio or tinker in the storage shed. With a deep garage and loads of off street parking, you are able to accommodate plenty of vehicles and extra guests. This home also features a newer roof, freshly done foundation work with a transferable warranty, and much more! 

Location is a winner with this home! You will enjoy quick highway access without sacrificing the quiet and peaceful feel of the neighborhood. Plus it's a hop, skip, and jump away from the Belton Community Center which has soccer fields, basketball and tennis courts and more to enjoy! Whether you're hitting the highways, shopping centers, or local parks, everything's within easy reach.

Schedule a showing today and make this your next home!
